623/**
624 * \def LDNS_RDATA_FIELD_DESCRIPTORS_COUNT
625 * computes the number of rdata fields
626 */
627#define LDNS_RDATA_FIELD_DESCRIPTORS_COUNT \
628 (sizeof(rdata_field_descriptors)/sizeof(rdata_field_descriptors[0]))
629
630const sldns_rr_descriptor *
631sldns_rr_descript(uint16_t type)
632{
633 size_t i;
634 if (type < LDNS_RDATA_FIELD_DESCRIPTORS_COMMON) {
635 return &rdata_field_descriptors[type];
636 } else {
637 /* because not all array index equals type code */
638 for (i = LDNS_RDATA_FIELD_DESCRIPTORS_COMMON;
639 i < LDNS_RDATA_FIELD_DESCRIPTORS_COUNT;
640 i++) {
641 if (rdata_field_descriptors[i]._type == type) {
642 return &rdata_field_descriptors[i];
643 }
644 }
645 return &rdata_field_descriptors[0];
646 }
647}

653 return descriptor->_minimum;
654 } else {
655 return 0;

659size_t
660sldns_rr_descriptor_maximum(const sldns_rr_descriptor *descriptor)
661{
662 if (descriptor) {
663 if (descriptor->_variable != LDNS_RDF_TYPE_NONE) {
664 return 65535; /* cannot be more than 64k */
665 } else {
666 return descriptor->_maximum;
667 }
668 } else {
669 return 0;
670 }
671}

673sldns_rdf_type
674sldns_rr_descriptor_field_type(const sldns_rr_descriptor *descriptor,
675 size_t index)
676{
677 assert(descriptor != NULL);
678 assert(index < descriptor->_maximum
679 || descriptor->_variable != LDNS_RDF_TYPE_NONE);
680 if (index < descriptor->_maximum) {
681 return descriptor->_wireformat[index];
682 } else {
683 return descriptor->_variable;
684 }
685}
686
687sldns_rr_type
688sldns_get_rr_type_by_name(const char *name)
689{
690 unsigned int i;
691 const char *desc_name;
692 const sldns_rr_descriptor *desc;
693
694 /* TYPEXX representation */
695 if (strlen(name) > 4 && strncasecmp(name, "TYPE", 4) == 0) {
696 return atoi(name + 4);
697 }
698
699 /* Normal types */
700 for (i = 0; i < (unsigned int) LDNS_RDATA_FIELD_DESCRIPTORS_COUNT; i++) {
701 desc = &rdata_field_descriptors[i];
702 desc_name = desc->_name;
703 if(desc_name &&
704 strlen(name) == strlen(desc_name) &&
705 strncasecmp(name, desc_name, strlen(desc_name)) == 0) {
706 /* because not all array index equals type code */
707 return desc->_type;
708 }
709 }
710
711 /* special cases for query types */
712 if (strlen(name) == 4 && strncasecmp(name, "IXFR", 4) == 0) {
713 return 251;
714 } else if (strlen(name) == 4 && strncasecmp(name, "AXFR", 4) == 0) {
715 return 252;
716 } else if (strlen(name) == 5 && strncasecmp(name, "MAILB", 5) == 0) {
717 return 253;
718 } else if (strlen(name) == 5 && strncasecmp(name, "MAILA", 5) == 0) {
719 return 254;
720 } else if (strlen(name) == 3 && strncasecmp(name, "ANY", 3) == 0) {
721 return 255;
722 }
723
724 return 0;
725}

727sldns_rr_class
728sldns_get_rr_class_by_name(const char *name)
729{
730 sldns_lookup_table *lt;
731
732 /* CLASSXX representation */
733 if (strlen(name) > 5 && strncasecmp(name, "CLASS", 5) == 0) {
734 return atoi(name + 5);
735 }
736
737 /* Normal types */
738 lt = sldns_lookup_by_name(sldns_rr_classes, name);
739 if (lt) {
740 return lt->id;
741 }
742 return 0;
743}
